addToPosition(uint256,uint256).details: Add to an existing staking position Can only be called by spNFT's owner or operators

baseURI().details: Returns the base URI set via {_setBaseURI}. This will be automatically added as a prefix in {tokenURI} to each token's URI, or to the token ID if no specific URI is set for that token ID.

boost(uint256,uint256).details: Assign "amount" of boost points to a position Can only be called by the master-defined YieldBooster contract

createPosition(uint256,uint256).details: Create a staking position (spNFT) with an optional lockDuration

exists(uint256).details: Returns true if "tokenId" is an existing spNFT id

getMultiplierByBoostPoints(uint256,uint2.details: Returns bonus multiplier from YieldBooster contract for given "amount" (LP token staked) and "boostPoints" (result is *1e4)

getMultiplierByLockDuration(uint256).details: Returns expected multiplier for a "lockDuration" duration lock (result is *1e4)

getMultiplierSettings().details: Returns all multiplier settings for this contract

getPoolInfo().details: Returns general "pool" info for this contract

harvestPosition(uint256).details: Harvest from a staking position Can only be called by spNFT's owner or approved address

harvestPositionTo(uint256,address).details: Harvest from a staking position to "to" address Can only be called by spNFT's owner or approved address spNFT's owner must be a contract

harvestPositionsTo(uint256[],address).details: Harvest from multiple staking positions to "to" address Can only be called by spNFT's owner or approved address

hasDeposits().details: Returns true if this pool currently has deposits

isUnlocked().details: Returns true if emergency unlocks are activated on this pool or on the master

lockPosition(uint256,uint256).details: Lock a staking position (can be used to extend a lock) Can only be called by spNFT's owner or approved address

owner().details: Returns this contract's owner (= master contract's owner)

pendingRewards(uint256).details: Returns pending rewards for a position

renewLockPosition(uint256).details: Renew lock from a staking position Can only be called by spNFT's owner or approved address

setBoostMultiplierSettings(uint256,uint2.details: Set global and boost multiplier settings maxGlobalMultiplier must be <= MAX_GLOBAL_MULTIPLIER_LIMIT maxBoostMultiplier must be <= MAX_BOOST_MULTIPLIER_LIMIT (maxBoostMultiplier + _maxLockMultiplier) must be <= _maxGlobalMultiplier Must only be called by the owner

setEmergencyUnlock(bool).details: Set emergency unlock status Must only be called by the owner

setLockMultiplierSettings(uint256,uint25.details: Set lock multiplier settings maxLockMultiplier must be <= MAX_LOCK_MULTIPLIER_LIMIT maxLockMultiplier must be <= _maxGlobalMultiplier - _maxBoostMultiplier Must only be called by the owner

setOperator(address).details: Set operator (usually deposit token's project's owner) to adjust contract's settings Must only be called by the owner

setXTokenRewardsShare(uint256).details: Set the share of xToken for the distributed rewards The share of token will incidently be 100% - xTokenRewardsShare Must only be called by the owner

supportsInterface(bytes4).details: See {IERC165-supportsInterface}. Time complexity O(1), guaranteed to always use less than 30 000 gas.

unboost(uint256,uint256).details: Remove "amount" of boost points from a position Can only be called by the master-defined YieldBooster contract

updatePool().details: Updates rewards states of the given pool to be up-to-date

withdrawFromPosition(uint256,uint256).details: Withdraw from a staking position Can only be called by spNFT's owner or approved address

yieldBooster().details: Get master-defined yield booster contract address

emergencyWithdraw(uint256).notice: Withdraw without caring about rewards, EMERGENCY ONLY Can only be called by spNFT's owner
